-02-22T07:58:32.000Z","msg":"竟然係呢隻味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時餵流浪貓 <br />\n唔知點解沙甸魚好多貓都麻麻哋咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bc23822e1bc701cd04a93ba6b70b327bdcc54c","tid":2416910,"uid":147831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5b7b76e5dd565e1e3f8f29bc52619f94229723c","tid":2416910,"uid":157002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:19:47.000Z","msg":"開頭唔識野 以為啲罐差唔多就一直俾monpetit金裝佢食 <br />\n佢一直都會食哂既<br />\n去到早排先知原來呢隻罐唔好<br />\n同埋食開呢隻既話因為好重口味所以好難轉罐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完貓糧個post就買哂怪獸同汪喵既主副食罐俾佢試 但佢食都唔食..<br />\n上網睇其他人轉罐分享 <br />\n試咗好多方法（乾濕一齊俾/減乾糧份量再慢慢加新罐/新罐撈舊罐/取消乾糧放題）<br />\n全部都唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢勁硬頸唔食就唔食 而家越嚟越瘦<br />\n想問下有無人有其他成功轉罐方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:40:33.000Z","msg":"餓到就死就會知死肯食返"},{"pid":"32cb968788f93034d5c17174c98d6b615a8af524","tid":2416910,"uid":147831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ce372117443b55e0159533e486fa27b7f6dfcaf","tid":2416910,"uid":157002,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d1f02555e4c77afe6bde9cd2c39c9ad68338461","tid":2416910,"uid":344625,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"餓兩日 屎都照食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:34:46.000Z","msg":"佢真係寧願餓都唔食 淨係飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\