ease.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日去買其他罐試下先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:59:51.000Z","msg":"同我個隻一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實乾糧營養足夠，係可以唔洗濕糧<br />\n如果飲得唔夠水，想用濕糧補充<br />\n可以試下去買湯包，我最近買donki 既ciao 既雞加白飯魚湯包，佢飲D汁飲到好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又有水份補充"},{"pid":"2e3f9a2ae9dfaeee9c3caf7e0bf59963de749ff0","tid":2416910,"uid":141681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:01:36.000Z","msg":"跪喺到求佢食"},{"pid":"e03df06f40fe754c505ae7f6b5dd8be8a7884d82","tid":2416910,"uid":50032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9639124ed94f1ca1db19f3495d1ebeb7a60512a","tid":2416910,"uid":173988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e7ac3aeb3c72dfb92dc1f8af818ef962c736136b","tid":2416910,"uid":138197,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:37:03.000Z","msg":"話餓佢打佢鬧佢班仆街一定冇養過貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"我未養貓之前都係咁諗，養左先知啲貓係可以寧願餓死都唔食&hellip;<br />\n同埋有啲貓餓三四日就會身體機能出事<br />\n我之前新接隻貓頭四日唔肯食嘢，我真係驚到鼻哥窿都冇肉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:44:05.000Z","msg":"好彩我3隻貓b餓咗一日就肯食"},{"pid":"03c5b118e243bb67ef8f47b21cc4c0645943fce4","tid":2416910,"uid":88563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:56:36.000Z","msg":"魚都好濃味㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等佢食肥啲再俾佢試吓雞/牛/兔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d265e164b9081fd868737a05500ff3192d9df5a","tid":2416910,"uid":157002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f46dbebf12989b29c8a00dd59a121065771522f","tid":2416910,"uid":66063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b02ef23afc3c84f53242127f37a335adba01ccc1","tid":2416910,"uid":157002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9df436d42ad4ddb13b8832d2522be53ebb47652a","tid"